Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.61,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:07.36,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was a bright, \Nclear day, just like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.25,flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bell, come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.41,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,They said my grandfather was attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.18,internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,by a monster in the mountains and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:24.79,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,They said he fell into a deep valley \Nwhere we couldn't go to search for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.20,flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,I've made my decision, grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:36.22,flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:52.03,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,But I looked so weak that \Nno familia would accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:53.39,flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.62,flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We won't feed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.00,flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You could do the cleaning, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.45,flashback,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better have your own money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.05,flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me into your familia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.87,flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Come back when you get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:09.95,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.65,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for a familia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.68,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,There was a goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:23.01,internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,...standing in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.64,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,My goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.60,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.83,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You should run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.96,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Bell-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.45,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:47.68,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:51.23,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose any more family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:53.09,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.57,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:05.39,Main Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(4111,1)}Is It Wrong to Try to\N Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.56,Ep Title,H,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(312,310)}Hestia Knife\N{\fs26}The Blade of a God
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:30.63,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Some monsters escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:31.98,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What about the guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:36.64,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They all looked like they had\Ntheir souls sucked out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.98,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We think someone from the \Noutside is responsible, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.78,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We can worry about that later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.73,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How many monsters escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:44.86,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.56,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our familia's strike force \Nwent into action immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.11,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't deal with it\Nquickly enough by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.37,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work with the other familia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.77,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Ask the other gods here for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.84,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:01.30,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It was we, the Ganesha Familia, \Nwho let those monsters escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.51,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If we have to rely on other familia \Nfor help, we'll be humiliated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.29,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ganesha, the lord of the masses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.11,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our greatest happiness is \Nseeing our children smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.77,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Forget your desire\Nfor position and honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:16.63,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our highest priority is \Nthe safety of the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.33,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:21.19,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,To avoid confusion,\Nwe're going to let the festival continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.99,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let this problem get any bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.88,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.95,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.55,internal/narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:39.09,internal/narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A diversion? Confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.59,internal/narrator,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.34,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.23,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Hestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.70,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:15.71,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,The hieroglyphs you carved into\N that knife gave it a status of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.92,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,That weapon is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.88,flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:25.05,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes into the hands \Nof your child, Bell Cranel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.99,flashback,L,0000,0000,0000,,it will come alive for the first time,\N and it will grow as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.76,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.87,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.19,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.90,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.58,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody from the Ganesha \NFamilia was saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,monsters escaped at the west gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.44,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.27,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,What if you cause a panic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.08,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.74,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, they said if there \Nare any adventurers nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,ask them for help, no matter \Nwhat familia they're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.37,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,But the odds of any being around are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.33,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,What, you guys got a way to make some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.53,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.34,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Sword Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.22,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Aiz Wallenstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:39.67,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the goddess got away okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.01,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And Aiz-san isn't coming this time, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.84,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.27,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I'm lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.23,internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,she won't see me like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.05,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.87,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Aiz-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.62,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,How many monsters are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.36,top,Background,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, you don't have to be so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.84,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,We've asked other adventurers for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are probably three or four more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.09,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.15,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,The Sword Princess really \Nis amazing, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:41.10,main,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can kind of see why\NBell-kun admires her so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.70,internal/narrator,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not caught up in all this, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.30,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.28,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.86,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.73,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.83,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.42,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.47,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:19.47,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:23.09,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.09,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.71,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.57,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You really are hopeless, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:33.32,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd run and leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.98,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You want to protect me, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.24,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll say the exact same thing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.96,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,And you promised me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.89,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.50,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.99,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.30,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate we're both going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.53,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.99,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.37,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.96,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.88,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything that's \Ngoing on, I'm incredibly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.81,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.44,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.53,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's after you, Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.43,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until he finds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.00,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's change our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.39,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, Bell-kun, you'll defeat that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.71,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'll update your status right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.42,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hit that monster with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.42,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.44,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm a little stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:24.43,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,my attacks aren't enough \Nto kill that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:25.96,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.60,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.78,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.45,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start being so pessimistic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.16,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.01,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I mean, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:45.37,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Bell Cranel I know, \Nwho's in love with that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,monstrous Wallenwhatsit woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.71,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,could defeat that monster easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.65,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.83,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.48,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.97,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Your, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.14,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Our weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.94,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.17,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Hestia Knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.67,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring you victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.70,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.45,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Please, will you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:28.66,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.47,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the last \Nof them, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.18,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,And now Ganesha owes me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.72,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The silverback is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:52.92,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A witness saw it chasing a young \Nadventurer down Daedalus Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.24,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus Street? Of all the places...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.06,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:59.40,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Ganesha Familia's\Nstrike force went after it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.30,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but given what that place is like, \Nthey can't even find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.29,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.83,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Aiz-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.98,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,This knife has that power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:37.38,flashback,He,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.49,flashback,He,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's the perfect \Nweapon for a new adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.03,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.45,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Divine Smith of Heaven,\N Hephaestus, for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.34,flashback,He,0000,0000,0000,,Your flattery won't take a \Nsingle valis off your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.52,flashback,He,0000,0000,0000,,But from a blacksmith's perspective, \Na weapon like this is totally wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.47,flashback,He,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me make another one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.14,flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.67,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hephaestus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:09.04,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,The question is how much \NBell-kun's status has gone up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.46,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.06,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,His ability score total is over 600 points?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.42,internal/narrator,H,0000,0000,0000,,This will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.03,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.52,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Bell-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.94,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.32,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.32,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.58,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You'll believe in me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:12.83,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.12,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.47,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.72,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,That is your power right now, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.69,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,That knife is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:38.78,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The more its wielder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.66,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The more you grow,\Nthe stronger it will become!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.41,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The more I grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.74,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...that knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.12,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.59,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,And believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.50,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.99,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.26,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.06,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.69,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,For my goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.36,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I di—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.78,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.36,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.07,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.09,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.41,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.17,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.88,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line, Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.84,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.34,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:42.06,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I chased after your butt...\NAs fast as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.62,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.98,main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we should take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.95,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,This got really big, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.72,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:56.91,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.99,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.33,internal/narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,G...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.22,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.79,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that wasn't a very \Nnice thing to do to Hestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.39,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play again sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.74,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.46,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,but you all did great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.41,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Ganesha is extremely satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.70,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way, I'm Ganesha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.62,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:51.30,internal/narrator,E,0000,0000,0000,,No fatalities or serious injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.94,internal/narrator,E,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.72,internal/narrator,E,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know who did this or why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.15,main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:22.83,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,How is your goddess doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.35,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's just tired and resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.27,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.50,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You even lent us a bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.29,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help each other with trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.62,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mama Mia said it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.01,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:43.06,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This only happened because \NI forgot my wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.02,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you got caught up in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.93,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.44,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not your fault, Syr-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:51.88,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.10,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,All the townspeople said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you were very heroic when \Nyou fought the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:00.41,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... All I did was run around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.11,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.34,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I saw a little of it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.74,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,And I fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.40,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go help in the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.22,main,S,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Bell-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.14,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was she making fun of me, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.56,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.51,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Bell-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.73,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:37.17,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me when you \Njust collapsed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.88,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the exhaustion caught up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.57,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.26,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Syr-san and the other waitresses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:49.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,that all the monsters besides that \Nsilverback were also defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.58,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Aiz Wallenstein-san was\Na big part of it, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.14,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.37,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.30,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get this knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:02.52,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,On the scabbard it says "Hephaestus"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.26,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Is that—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.48,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It was that Hephaestus, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.00,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.80,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how you always used \Nto have your face pressed up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,against the glass of her shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:19.61,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It may not have been what you wanted, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.44,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only one \Nof its kind in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:25.37,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.50,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.87,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Or you to just take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.29,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Or just to have you save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.97,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.80,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons from the Hephaestus \NFamilia are really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.70,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I worked something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.78,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to get stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.71,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'd help, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.44,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.48,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,More than anyone, more than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.30,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.07,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.49,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:06.03,main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:08.75,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,You can always rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.92,main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.03,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:21.88,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.31,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.85,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless as a supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.21,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no money for somebody \Nwho just slows me down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:33.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and can't do her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:38.43,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we get surrounded by monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.27,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least use you as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.61,main,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Useless moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:30.18,main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about this, Hephaestus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.05,main,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
